During the next five years, I started a company named NeXT another company namedPixar,and fell in with an amazing woman who would become my wife.Pixar is now the most successful animation studio in the world. Steve Jobs’s life and this speech was really good. However I think I have to be careful to choose another way from other people, because he succeeded. If he failed, he never spoke to Havered Students. Now I’m looking for a job, so I wanna find what I wanna be.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
[2]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
[3] I find that it isn't always important to graduate college. There are many ways to live your own life .I think it is important to think about things from many different angles. I like his words . “Don’t waste it living someone else’s life.” “Don’t be trapped in dogma-which is living with the results of other people’ opinion. I always mind other people’s opinions so these words are the most important in my life . I learned to think what truly I want , follow my life will connect my future .                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
[4]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
[5] I was very impressed by the words, “If you love each day as if it was you last, someday you’ll most certainly be right.”. The speaker said that thinking about losing something helps us make big choices in life. I realized that I usually think but in fact, no one can be sure about tomorrow. This idea made me think more seriously about how I should spend my time. If I remember that today might be my last day, I will try to use every chance more carefully. I want to spend my days doing things that really matter to me, not wasting time on unimportant things. From now on, I hope to act with more courage and follow my true feelings. In this way, I believe I can live a more meaningful life and never regret the choices I make.
